  {
    "id": 2,
    "offset": 276030,
    "slot_size": 178,
    "data_size": 174,
    "nom_orig": "Ginko",
    "texte_orig": "Huh...?[1205][0014][SP]Why[SP]am[SP]I[SP]crying?[SP]It's[SP]so[SP]strange,\nbut...[SP]*sniff*[1205][0014][SP]I[SP]can't[SP]stop...",
