  {
    "id": 3,
    "offset": 276208,
    "slot_size": 236,
    "data_size": 232,
    "nom_orig": "Eikichi",
    "texte_orig": "It's...[1205][001E][SP]like[SP]a[SP]nice[SP]memory...[SP]Warmer[SP]than\nwhat[SP]I[SP]felt[SP]with[SP][U+1113][SP]and[SP]Ginko...[1205][001E]\nLike[SP]a[SP]hug[SP]from[SP]my[SP]mom...",
